* Needs to be able to read configuration from a config file.
  - config file needs to have livestats broker location
  - has to have default location under /etc/qlivestats.conf

* Needs to be able to connect to the livestatus broker socket.
* Needs to be able to query the livestats broker for services with filters and coulumns.
* Needs to be able to query the livestats broker for hosts with filters and coulumns.
* Needs to be able to query the livestats broker for logs with date filter.
* Needs to be able to get state history for both servers and hosts.
* Needs to be able to query nagios contacts

* Implement OR AND operators. 
